panels.description: Shows average, median, 15th and 85th percentiles for commits lines added, lines removed and files changed. Alerts: green: OK, blue - value too low, red - value too high.

targets.rawSql:
select
  avg(sub.loc_added) filter (where sub.loc_added > 0) as "Average LOC added",
  max(sub.loc_added) as "Max LOC added",
  percentile_cont(0.5) within group (order by sub.loc_added asc) filter (where sub.loc_added > 0) as "Median LOC added",
  percentile_cont(0.15) within group (order by sub.loc_added asc) filter (where sub.loc_added > 0) as "15th perc. LOC added",
  percentile_cont(0.85) within group (order by sub.loc_added asc) filter (where sub.loc_added > 0) as "85th perc. LOC added",
  avg(sub.loc_removed) filter (where sub.loc_removed > 0) as "Average LOC removed",
  max(sub.loc_removed) as "Max LOC removed",
  percentile_cont(0.5) within group (order by sub.loc_removed asc) filter (where sub.loc_removed > 0) as "Median LOC removed",
  percentile_cont(0.15) within group (order by sub.loc_removed asc) filter (where sub.loc_removed > 0) as "15th perc. LOC removed",
  percentile_cont(0.85) within group (order by sub.loc_removed asc) filter (where sub.loc_removed > 0) as "85th perc. LOC removed",
  avg(sub.files_changed) filter (where sub.files_changed > 0) as "Average files ch.",
  max(sub.files_changed) as "Max files ch.",
  percentile_cont(0.5) within group (order by sub.files_changed asc) filter (where sub.files_changed > 0) as "Median files ch.",
  percentile_cont(0.15) within group (order by sub.files_changed asc) filter (where sub.files_changed > 0) as "15th perc. files ch.",
  percentile_cont(0.85) within group (order by sub.files_changed asc) filter (where sub.files_changed > 0) as "85th perc. files ch."
from (
  select distinct
    c.sha,
    c.loc_added,
    c.loc_removed,
    c.files_changed
  from
    gha_commits c,
    gha_repos r
  where
    c.dup_repo_id = r.id
    and c.dup_repo_name = r.name
    and r.repo_group in ([[repogroups]])
    and c.loc_added is not null
    and c.loc_removed is not null
    and c.files_changed is not null
    and $__timeFilter(c.dup_created_at)
    and (c.dup_author_login in ([[contributors]]) or '[[contributors:csv]]' = 'null')
    and lower(c.dup_author_login) not like all(array['devstats-sync', 'googlebot', 'coveralls', 'rktbot', 'coreosbot', 'web-flow', 'prometheus-roobot', 'cncf-bot', 'kernelprbot', 'istio-testing', 'spinnakerbot', 'pikbot', 'spinnaker-release', 'docker-jenkins', 'golangcibot', 'opencontrail-ci-admin', 'k8s-%', '%-bot', '%-robot', 'bot-%', 'robot-%', '%[bot]%', '%-jenkins', '%-ci%bot', '%-testing', 'codecov-%', '%clabot%', '%cla-bot%', '%-gerrit', '%-bot-%'])
) sub

panels.title: Last month LOC statistics

panels.description: Number of distinct commits modifying files with a given extension during the last month

targets.rawSql:
select
  now() as "time",
  count(distinct ecf.sha) as "value",
  ecf.ext as "name"
from
  gha_events_commits_files ecf,
  gha_events e,
  gha_repos r
where
  e.id = ecf.event_id
  and e.repo_id = r.id
  and e.dup_repo_name = r.name
  and r.repo_group in ([[repogroups]])
  and $__timeFilter(e.created_at)
  and ecf.ext not like '%/%'
  and ecf.ext != ''
  and (e.dup_actor_login in ([[contributors]]) or '[[contributors:csv]]' = 'null')
  and lower(e.dup_actor_login) not like all(array['devstats-sync', 'googlebot', 'coveralls', 'rktbot', 'coreosbot', 'web-flow', 'prometheus-roobot', 'cncf-bot', 'kernelprbot', 'istio-testing', 'spinnakerbot', 'pikbot', 'spinnaker-release', 'docker-jenkins', 'golangcibot', 'opencontrail-ci-admin', 'k8s-%', '%-bot', '%-robot', 'bot-%', 'robot-%', '%[bot]%', '%-jenkins', '%-ci%bot', '%-testing', 'codecov-%', '%clabot%', '%cla-bot%', '%-gerrit', '%-bot-%'])
group by
  ecf.ext
order by
  "value" desc
limit 50

panels.description: Chart for all LOC statistics for all days during the last month. Displays 30th and 70th percentiles.

targets.rawSql:
select
  floor(extract(epoch from dup_created_at)/86400)*86400 AS "time",
  percentile_cont(0.7) within group (order by loc_added asc) as "70th percentile LOC added daily",
  percentile_cont(0.3) within group (order by loc_added asc) as "30th percentile LOC added daily"
from
  gha_commits c,
  gha_repos r
where
  c.dup_repo_id = r.id
  and c.dup_repo_name = r.name
  and r.repo_group in ([[repogroups]])
  and (c.dup_author_login in ([[contributors]]) or '[[contributors:csv]]' = 'null')
  and lower(c.dup_author_login) not like all(array['devstats-sync', 'googlebot', 'coveralls', 'rktbot', 'coreosbot', 'web-flow', 'prometheus-roobot', 'cncf-bot', 'kernelprbot', 'istio-testing', 'spinnakerbot', 'pikbot', 'spinnaker-release', 'docker-jenkins', 'golangcibot', 'opencontrail-ci-admin', 'k8s-%', '%-bot', '%-robot', 'bot-%', 'robot-%', '%[bot]%', '%-jenkins', '%-ci%bot', '%-testing', 'codecov-%', '%clabot%', '%cla-bot%', '%-gerrit', '%-bot-%'])
  and loc_added is not null
  and loc_added > 0
  and $__timeFilter(dup_created_at)
group by
  "time"
order by
  "time"

select

  percentile_cont(0.7) within group (order by loc_removed asc) as "70th percentile LOC removed daily",

  and loc_removed is not null
  and loc_removed > 0
  and $__timeFilter(dup_created_at)

select
  floor(extract(epoch from dup_created_at)/86400)*86400 AS "time",
  percentile_cont(0.7) within group (order by files_changed asc) as "70th percentile files changed daily",
  percentile_cont(0.3) within group (order by files_changed asc) as "30th percentile files changed daily"
from
  gha_commits c,
  gha_repos r
where
  c.dup_repo_id = r.id
  and c.dup_repo_name = r.name
  and r.repo_group in ([[repogroups]])
  and (c.dup_author_login in ([[contributors]]) or '[[contributors:csv]]' = 'null')
  and lower(c.dup_author_login) not like all(array['devstats-sync', 'googlebot', 'coveralls', 'rktbot', 'coreosbot', 'web-flow', 'prometheus-roobot', 'cncf-bot', 'kernelprbot', 'istio-testing', 'spinnakerbot', 'pikbot', 'spinnaker-release', 'docker-jenkins', 'golangcibot', 'opencontrail-ci-admin', 'k8s-%', '%-bot', '%-robot', 'bot-%', 'robot-%', '%[bot]%', '%-jenkins', '%-ci%bot', '%-testing', 'codecov-%', '%clabot%', '%cla-bot%', '%-gerrit', '%-bot-%'])
  and files_changed is not null
  and files_changed > 0
  and $__timeFilter(dup_created_at)
group by
  "time"
order by
  "time"
